rapped around 5.5 and 9 au and possibly open gaps,\nsome super-Earths trapped around 5 and 7.5 au and a population of close-in\nsuper-Earths trapped inside 1 au. The traps corresponding to the last group\ncould help validating the in-situ formation scenarios of the observed close-in\nsuper-Earths.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 24 Mar 2016 17:34:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 7 Apr 2016 08:41:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-11"}
